uple `(contract_version, stimulus_family,\\n+stimulus_name, parameter_hash)`. Later manifests and tooling should resolve\\n+stimuli through the library contract instead of hardcoded frame filenames.\\n+\\n+`docs/stimulus_bundle_design.md` is the authoritative Milestone 8A decision\\n+note; later tickets should cite it instead of re-litigating the representation\\n+family, replay semantics, or coordinate/luminance conventions.\\n \\n ### Offline operator QA contract\\nPATCH\\n\\ngit diff --cached --stat -- docs/pipeline_notes.md docs/stimulus_bundle_design.md src/flywire_wave/stimulus_contract.py tests/test_stimulus_contract.py'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"fatal: Unable to create '/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/.git/index.lock': Read-only file system\\nerror: corrupt patch at line 56\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nagent_tickets/runs/20260322T003533Z/FW-M8A-001_Freeze_a_versioned_stimulus_bundle_contract_and_canonical_generator_design_note/stdout.jsonl:106:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_60\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'git status --short'\",\"aggregated_output\":\" M Makefile\\n M README.md\\n M config/milestone_6_verification.yaml\\n M config/visual_subset.example.yaml\\n M docs/pipeline_notes.md\\n M scripts/03_build_wave_assets.py\\n M scripts/build_registry.py\\n M src/flywire_wave/__init__.py\\n M src/flywire_wave/config.py\\n M src/flywire_wave/geometry_contract.py\\n M src/flywire_wave/registry.py\\n M src/flywire_wave/selection.py\\n M tests/test_config_paths.py\\n M tests/test_geometry_contract.py\\n M tests/test_registry.py\\n M tests/test_selection.py\\n?? agent_tickets/milestone_8a_canonical_stimulus_library_tickets.md\\n?? agent_tickets/milestone_8b_retinal_ommatidial_sampler_tickets.md\\n?? agent_tickets/runs/20260321T222203Z/\\n?? agent_tickets/runs/20260322T003533Z/\\n?? config/milestone_7_verification.yaml\\n?? config/milestone_7_verific